data.description: Charming 4 bedroom in desirable Maplewood South.Lovingly maintained by owner for over 50 years!NEVER FLOODED.Beautiful curb appeal.Spacious formal living/dining.Kitchen has been updated w/white cabinets,tile floors,double ovens,pantry,ample storage space & eat-in breakfast room.Den boasts beamed ceiling,gas fireplace,hardwoods & built-ins.Over sized primary w/ two large closets-one a walk-in plus a door that leads out to covered patio.Primary bath features vanity,granite counter tops & shower.Three additional generous size bedrooms each w/walk-in closet.Hall bath well maintained w/tub & shower combination.Ample storage throughout. 5 bonus closets in the hallway.Utility room inside home features half bath & cabinets. Covered patio looks out to beautiful views of the back yard. 2 car over sized garage!Updates include: foundation repaired w/lifetime warranty,new hot water heater, updated electrical & new breaker box & whole home surge protector,gas meter redone, some PEX & much more!
